Show HN:Are you looking to furnish a space for a specific budget? We can help!
text:
Hi,

I'm searching for honest feedback about my new service. I am trying to help people with furnish. Basically, I give an online shopping list with direct links to online sources for every product local to purchase furniture. I also negotiate with the suppliers for a lower price.

Any feedback (web content, the business itself, etc. ) is acceptable and important!

Thank you for your valuable opinion.

Ask HN: Is it possible to setup a VPN server on iOS?
text: I've searched the internet and found no clue as to whether this is possible on iOS. I know Android supports that (at least with root access), but I haven't seen any evidence that it's doable on iOS. Running a personal VPN server on iOS could help friends in other countries who suffer from super restricted internet access.
